name: ALIENATED (clonethirteen)
description:
This was for a jam that came and went. Life got busy with a multitude of things a month or more ago and I'm just now getting around to finishing this project.  

Controls - WASD to move around. Space to shoot.

Follow instructions on the screen to play. Enjoy and let me know what you think in the comments.

Music was by Zero - you can find it here https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCD2iUVkyqfuAFvqpdWweTkw.
